Figure 3 — TSLA: Parameter Sensitivity Study (2160 Configurations)

TSLA exhibits strong parameter sensitivity; shorter lookbacks (L=20) tend to perform better in this sample. Only 5.6% of 2160 tested configurations exceed the market's Sharpe ratio. Improvements are associated with higher exposure and turnover trade-offs.
